---
// src/pages/cafe/ice-cream.astro
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Homemade Ice Cream in Centerville | The Local Place Cafe"
  description="Creamy, rich homemade ice cream in Centerville. Made fresh, rotating flavors, real ingredients. Visit The Local Place Cafe at 111 S Public Square or order online."
  keywords="homemade ice cream Centerville, ice cream shop, fresh ice cream, local ice cream TN"
>
  <!-- Schema markup placeholder for LocalBusiness + Menu -->
  <!-- TODO: Add JSON-LD schema for ice cream offerings -->

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Homemade Ice Cream Worth the Trip</h1>
      <p>Creamy, Rich, Made Fresh. This Isn't Soft-Serve</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cafe">Cafe</a></li>
        <li><span>Ice Cream</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Real Ice Cream, Made Here</h2>
      <p>
        This isn't the stuff from a truck. We make it here. Real cream, real sugar, real vanilla. Dense, creamy, scoopable ice cream that melts on your tongue. The kind you remember eating as a kid—if you were lucky enough to have good ice cream as a kid.
      </p>

      <h3>Rotating Flavors</h3>
      <p>
        We don't make 47 flavors and let them sit. We make small batches, rotate them out, and keep it fresh. Ask what's available—it changes, and that's the point.
      </p>

      <div class="menu-items">
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Classic Vanilla Bean</h4>
          <p>Real vanilla beans. Creamy, rich, not bland. This is what vanilla should taste like.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Chocolate</h4>
          <p>Deep, rich, chocolatey. Not too sweet. Just right.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Salted Caramel</h4>
          <p>Sweet caramel with a hint of salt. Buttery, smooth, addictive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Strawberry</h4>
          <p>Made with real strawberries, not artificial flavoring. Fresh, fruity, creamy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Mint Chocolate Chip</h4>
          <p>Fresh mint, real chocolate chips. Not neon green. Tastes like actual mint.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Coffee</h4>
          <p>Made with our own espresso. Rich, bold, for coffee lovers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Cookies & Cream</h4>
          <p>Chunks of real Oreos. Creamy vanilla base. A classic done right.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Seasonal Flavors</h4>
          <p>Pumpkin spice in fall, peppermint in winter, peach in summer. Whatever's fresh.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Serving Options</h3>
      <div class="menu-items">
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Single Scoop</h4>
          <p>One generous scoop in a cup or cone. Enough to satisfy.</p>
          <span class="price">$4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Double Scoop</h4>
          <p>Two scoops, your choice of flavors. Mix and match.</p>
          <span class="price">$6</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Pint to Go</h4>
          <p>Take a whole pint home. Perfect for sharing. Or not.</p>
          <span class="price">$7</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Why Our Ice Cream Tastes Better</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Made in-house:</strong> We control every ingredient. No shortcuts.</li>
        <li><strong>Real ingredients:</strong> Real cream, real vanilla, real fruit. No artificial anything.</li>
        <li><strong>Small batches:</strong> Fresh, never sitting in a freezer for months.</li>
        <li><strong>Dense and creamy:</strong> This is ice cream, not frozen air.</li>
        <li><strong>Rotating flavors:</strong> Something new to try every visit.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Perfect Any Time of Year</h3>
      <p>
        Ice cream in January? Absolutely. Ice cream after lunch? Why not. Ice cream because it's Tuesday? We're not judging. Come in, grab a scoop, sit down, enjoy it.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Try It Today</h3>
        <p>Stop by and ask what flavors are fresh. You can sample before you commit.</p>
        <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" class="cta-button">Order Online</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>What Customers Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"The vanilla bean is unreal. I thought vanilla was boring until I tried this. Rich, creamy, you can see the beans. Now I get it every time."</p>
          <p><strong>- Sarah (Regular)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"My kids beg to come here for ice cream. We've tried every flavor—salted caramel is my favorite, cookies and cream is theirs. It's all good."</p>
          <p><strong>- The Martinez Family</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"I grabbed a double scoop after lunch and it was the best decision I made all week. Coffee and chocolate—both rich, both perfect."</p>
          <p><strong>- Jake (Visitor)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="location-info">
      <h2>Visit The Local Place Cafe</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Hours</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 6 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Saturday:</strong> 9 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>
            111 South Public Square<br />
            Centerville, TN 37033<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-3481">(931) 729-3481</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Order Online</h3>
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Order on Clover →</a><br />
            Pick up fresh ice cream.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #a8d8d8 0%, #7ab8ba 100%);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .menu-items {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .menu-item {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .menu-item h4 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .menu-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .price {
    display: block;
    color: #8b4513;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-box h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #6b3410;
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p:first-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .testimonial-card p:last-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .location-info {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .info-block {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .info-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .info-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .info-block a {
    color: var(--brown);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .info-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .menu-items {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
